quran[31]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,40,"Jannooyin (beero gudahood) waxay iska wareysan,"
  74,41,"Xaalka denbiilayaasha:"
  74,42,"Maxaa idin keenay Naarta Saqaro?"
  75,37,"Miyuusan aheyn mani-nool oo la dhibciyo?"
  75,38,"Markaas noqota xinjir oo (Alle) abuuro qaab wanaagsanna u yeelo."
  75,39,"Oo ka yeelo labo nooc, lab iyo dheddig."
  76,31,"Wuxuu geliyaa qofkuu doono Naxariistiisa, daalimiintana (mushrikiinta, gaalada, denbiilayaasha) Wuxuu u diyaariyey cadaab xanuun badan."
  77,28,"Hoog Maalintaas waxaa leh xaq beeniyayaasha (nabad diidka)."
  77,29,"Aada waxaad beenin jirteen."
  77,30,"Aada hoos (qiiqa Naarta ah) oo seddex laamood leh{2}.",footnotes:1:[. Xagga seddex jiho: Midigta, bidixda, iyo dusha sare, macnaha waa cadaabka wuxuu uga iman oo ka hareereyn gaalada jiho kasta.],footnotes:2:[]
  78,25,"Biyo kulul oo karaya iyo malax maahee (dhacaanka ehlu Naarka ah)"
  78,26,"Waa abaal marin ku habboon (gaalada)."
  78,27,"Waxay ahaayeen kuwo aan fileyn Xisaab (Aakhiro)."
  79,19,"Oo aan kugu hanuunsho xagga (Alle) Rabbigaa si aad uga baqdo?."
  79,20,"Markaasuu tusay Calaamddii Weyneyd (gacantii ifeysay ama ushii maska weyn noqoneysay)."
  79,21,"(Fircoon) se wuu beeniyey oo caasiyey."
  80,16,"Sharaf leh oo baariyaal ah."
  80,17,"Belo ha ku dhacdo aadmigee (waa kan gaalka ahi)! Muxuu jazaar yahay!"
  80,18,"Muxuu Alle ka abuuray?"
  81,13,"Oo Jannada la soo dhoweeyo."
  81,14,"Waxay ogaan nafi waxay la timid (khayr ama shar)."
  81,15,"Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay xiddigaha qarsooma (maalintii)."
  82,7,"Kaasoo ku abuuray, kuna ekeeyey oo ku simay?"
  82,8,"Suuradduu doonana kuu sameeyey?."
  82,9,"Mayee bal waxaad beenisaan maalinta is abaal marinta (jaazeynta)."
  83,4,"Miyeyna u malaynaynin kuwaasi in loo soo bixin doono (si loo xisaabiyo)."
  83,5,"Maalin weyn (Qiyaamada)."
  83,6,"Maalinta dadku istaagi Rabbiga uumanka horti?"
  84,1,"Markay samadu dildillaacdo (Qiyaamada)."
  84,2,"Oo ay adeecdo Rabbigeed, waana xaq inay adeecdo;"
  84,3,"Marka arlada la fidiyo,"
